messages.message: Hi team, when uploading a Dutch payslip, I get weird field suggestions, many of them have the same field name and value build/08ca1f89-bbca-4f8f-aa57-5e970418ee15

What I would expect are fields like date, net pay, gross pay etc. Instead I am seeing "pay including holiday allowance" with the value "pay including holiday allowance" and "Job title SAP" with value "Job title SAP"
ah interesting, we will add this to our benchmarks
what would be 5-10 of the expected field suggestions and values (in dutch)?
The field values looks like provenance line numbers. This is likely because the LLM reply format was not same as we asked.
